    "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><img src=\"images/101_content_0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\"></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Top 2025 priorities for savvy homeowners: &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Efficiency Upgrades</strong>: Water-saving fixtures &amp; energy-smart lighting &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Wellness Integration</strong>: Steam showers, heated floors, anti-slip surfaces &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Universal Design</strong>: Curbless showers &amp; grab bars for multi-gen living &nbsp;<em>Pro Tip: 68% of U.S. buyers prioritize updated bathrooms (NAR survey).</em>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>&nbsp;TREND ALERT: MATERIALS THAT LAST</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;Choose surfaces combining style + resilience: &nbsp;➤ <strong>Porcelain Slabs</strong>&nbsp;(replacing tiles for seamless look) &nbsp;➤ <strong>Quartz Countertops</strong>&nbsp;(stain/mold-resistant) &nbsp;➤ <strong>Waterproof Luxury Vinyl</strong>&nbsp;(wood-look without warping) &nbsp;<em>Avoid: High-maintenance grout lines + porous natural stone.</em>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>&nbsp;NAVIGATING YOUR RENOVATION: KEY STEPS</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Plan Smart</strong>: &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]-->Measure space &rarr; Sketch layout (include double sinks? freestanding tub?) &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]-->Research <em>ENERGY STAR&reg;</em>&nbsp;fixtures for utility rebates &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Hire Confidently</strong>: &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]-->Verify contractor license + IICRC water damage certification &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]-->Request 3D renderings before demolition &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Execute Flawlessly</strong>: &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]-->Sequence: Demolition &rarr; Plumbing &rarr; Waterproofing &rarr; Tile &rarr; Fixtures &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]-->Inspect moisture barriers before closing walls &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">⚠️ AVOID THESE COMMON MISTAKES</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Poor Ventilation</strong>: Install humidity-sensing exhaust fans (code requirement in 32 states) &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Ignoring Codes</strong>: Permits for electrical/plumbing changes are non-negotiable &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Trend Overload</strong>: Stick with timeless elements (neutral tiles) + trendy <em>accents</em>&nbsp;(brushed gold faucets) &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>&nbsp;SUSTAINABLE FOCUS: 2025 INNOVATIONS</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Greywater Systems</strong>: Recycle shower water for toilets &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><strong>Pre-fab Wall Panels</strong>: Reduce construction waste by 75% vs. tile &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12p